xt": "how will it be to them when it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(the hour)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cometh to them with their remembrance and their reception of exhortation:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, * TA:) i. e., this will not profit them. (TA.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Repentance:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "so in the Kur [lxxxix. 24],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waA^an~aY lahu Al*~ikoraY", "text_ar": "وَاَنَّى لَهُ الذِّكْرَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And how shall he have repentance?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA.) ―         -b4-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A reminding,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "causing to remember:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "so in the Kur viii. 1, and xi. 121, (K,) and li. 55. (Fr.) See 2. ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An admonition:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "so in the Kur xxxviii. 42, and xl. 56. (K.) ―         -b6-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A being reminded,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "caused to remember:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "so in the Kur [xxxviii. 46], in the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "*ikoraY Ald~aAri", "text_ar": "ذِكْرَى الدَّارِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "Their"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "being reminded of,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "caused to remember, the"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "latter"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abode,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and being made to relinquish worldly things, or not to desire them: (K:) or it may mean their"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "remembering much the latter abode."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(B, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["K"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}